(695, 'event', '65', 'comment', 'EN', '<p>The stick of Captain Larralde and sub-lieutenant Quillet was dropped at the same time as the Jedburg team Dicing charged with recruiting and training Dutch patriots in the Hooghalen sector.</p>', 'paul golder', '2010-10-06 14:28:01'),
